(Yeah, I should've mentioned the names, I just didn't have their profiles 
anywhere and hadn't used them in so long I'd forgotten :)  But now that I'm 
home I've got files with their profiles in 'em, so anyway...)

The Protectobots:



Hot Spot lead the Autobot gestalt team, leaping into the air as he close to 
Prowl's proximity.  He crashed back to the ground hard as a blue firetruck, 
powering up his cannon as he drove off at 30 MPH.

"Hurry up guys, who knows what the situation is!"

"Now, now, Hot Spot, for all we know this is just something that could be 
solved with words rather than fisticuffs!" Groove's, second in command of the 
Protectobots, voice said, its source a police motorcycle following the blue 
firetruck.

"Peace is fine and dandy," Blades said, leaping a good dozen feet into the 
air, his form twisting and contorting into a white, red, and yellow AH-64 
Apache Attack Helicopter, arming a pair of rockets, "but if those are Preds 
they'll have more to worry about then words, Groove."

A white ambulance barreled down after them, a brown Autobot insignia on his 
hood.  "Try not to get to damaged though!  Be sure to make sure no civilians 
are in the area either, they don't deserve to be harmed." First Aid, 
doctor/medic of the team, said.


"Don't worry, First Aid," Streetwise in his police car mode said, "I'll 
notice any innocents in the vacinity before we start shooting."
